thread.title: BRIEF-Fannie Mae Book Of Business Increased At Compound Annualized Rate Of 2.7 Pct In January 2018

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Fannie Mae Book Of Business Increased At Compound Annualized Rate Of 2.7 Pct In January 2018
text:
Feb 28 (Reuters) - Federal National Mortgage Association :
* FANNIE MAE - FANNIE MAE‘S BOOK OF BUSINESS INCREASED AT A COMPOUND ANNUALIZED RATE OF 2.7 PERCENT IN JANUARY 2018
* FANNIE MAE - COMPLETED 7,285 LOAN MODIFICATIONS IN JANUARY‍​
* FANNIE MAE - CONVENTIONAL SINGLE-FAMILY SERIOUS DELINQUENCY RATE DECREASED 1 BASIS POINT TO 1.23% IN JANUARY 2018
* FANNIE MAE - MULTIFAMILY SERIOUS DELINQUENCY RATE REMAINED FLAT AT 0.11%‍​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
